<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Notification:</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">It has been 7 days since the Share class&nbsp;{!Share_Class__c.Name}&nbsp;{!Share_Class__c.</span>ISIN_Code__c<span style="font-size: 12pt;">}</span></font><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;was closed.</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Please note that within 5 days the Share Class will be removed from all the WTPs, otherwise you have to reactivate the Share Class or replace it by another one.</div>]]></td>
